  "detailed_description": "In <strong>Roguelike Chess</strong>, you become another piece on the world's board, but with a difference: You are special, you have a vision of the board, you know the rules and you know exactly what to do: <strong> DESTROY ENEMIES!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/234d37e0d8c4831d937a074c935bda8c.poster.avif?t=1708607743\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/234d37e0d8c4831d937a074c935bda8c.webm?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/234d37e0d8c4831d937a074c935bda8c.mp4?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You start as a simple piece that can move one square to each side, but each round, you can buy a card to gain abilities that range from moving one more square at a time to attacking from a distance or an extra life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/2c83c7c405dfd4eeedeba0a92631d648.poster.avif?t=1708607743\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/2c83c7c405dfd4eeedeba0a92631d648.webm?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/2c83c7c405dfd4eeedeba0a92631d648.mp4?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Customize your game with the various skins from the store purchased with money purchased within the game:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/3db81771bdf0ab32c1cbc9f1099247d6.poster.avif?t=1708607743\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/3db81771bdf0ab32c1cbc9f1099247d6.webm?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/3db81771bdf0ab32c1cbc9f1099247d6.mp4?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/94a97cf14ce25eec328849582c60c605.poster.avif?t=1708607743\" width=640 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/94a97cf14ce25eec328849582c60c605.webm?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/94a97cf14ce25eec328849582c60c605.mp4?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Improve your strategy, think about each move and advance as much as you can by facing more pieces through turns:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/a9c9b861526f9b59fab48269351a7ce3.poster.avif?t=1708607743\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/a9c9b861526f9b59fab48269351a7ce3.webm?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/a9c9b861526f9b59fab48269351a7ce3.mp4?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose the scenario you want as the battlefield:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/18505a68c16ffe0cc59a7d475429fef6.poster.avif?t=1708607743\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/18505a68c16ffe0cc59a7d475429fef6.webm?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/18505a68c16ffe0cc59a7d475429fef6.mp4?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/03b5971c5664a2e1bd7203e72ffe04a7.poster.avif?t=1708607743\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/03b5971c5664a2e1bd7203e72ffe04a7.webm?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/03b5971c5664a2e1bd7203e72ffe04a7.mp4?t=1708607743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
